hopobject.body: What's the exchange rate for euros? meloxicam 7.5 vs ibuprofen If you don't already have health insurance through your employer, the new health care law's individual mandate requires that you purchase your own health insurance by Jan. 1, 2014. To make doing so a little easier, state-run health care marketplaces will open on Oct. 1, offering consumers a variety of choices. An estimated 18.6 million uninsured women are eligible to buy health insurance in these marketplaces , according to the Department of Health and Human Services .
